                  <div id="innerbodycontent" class="row nolayout"><div class="offset1 span10">
            <div id="sm-cog-elements" class="noprint"></div>
            <div class="allset-page-heading"><h1>Expressing "since the beginning" with "yixiang"</h1></div>
            <!-- subtitle -->
            <div id="contentSub" ></div>
            <!-- /subtitle -->
                        <div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div id="ibox" class="toc">
	<div class="ibox-link"><span class="plainlinks"><a href="ASGACMNQ" class="mw-redirect" title="ASGACMNQ"><img src="https&#58;//resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/silk/link.png" /></a></span></div>
	<ul class="ibox-list">
               <li class="ibox-level-cefr-hsk clearfix">
                        
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><span style="font-size: 1.4em;"><a href="B2_grammar_points" title="B2 grammar points"> B2</a></span> / <span style="font-size:0.75em;"><a href="HSK6_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK6 grammar points">HSK6</a></span></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level clearfix" style="display:none">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="B2_grammar_points" title="B2 grammar points"> B2</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="HSK6_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK6 grammar points"> HSK6</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Expressing_&quot;all_along&quot;_with_&quot;yizhi&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;all along&quot; with &quot;yizhi&quot;">Expressing "all along" with "yizhi"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">A2</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Comparing_&quot;yizhi&quot;_and_&quot;yixiang&quot;" title="Comparing &quot;yizhi&quot; and &quot;yixiang&quot;">Comparing "yizhi" and "yixiang"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">C1</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Expressing_&quot;all_along&quot;_with_&quot;yizhi&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;all along&quot; with &quot;yizhi&quot;">Expressing "all along" with "yizhi"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK3</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Comparing_&quot;yizhi&quot;_and_&quot;yixiang&quot;" title="Comparing &quot;yizhi&quot; and &quot;yixiang&quot;">Comparing "yizhi" and "yixiang"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK6</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-usedfor clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Used for</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="Referring_to_habitual_actions" title="Referring to habitual actions">Referring to habitual actions</a>, <a href="Referring_to_the_past" title="Referring to the past">Referring to the past</a>, <a href="Expressing_frequency" title="Expressing frequency">Expressing frequency</a>, <a href="Expressing_time_and_date" title="Expressing time and date">Expressing time and date</a> </div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-keywords clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Keywords</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="一向" title="一向">一向</a></div>
		</li>
		
	</ul>
	<div class="ibox-image"><a href="./File:Chinese-grammar-wiki-yixiang.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Chinese-grammar-wiki-yixiang.jpg" src="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/d/d1/Chinese-grammar-wiki-yixiang.jpg/300px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-yixiang.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/d/d1/Chinese-grammar-wiki-yixiang.jpg/450px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-yixiang.jpg 1.5x, https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/d/d1/Chinese-grammar-wiki-yixiang.jpg/600px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-yixiang.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</div> 
<p>一向 (yīxiàng) means "<a href="Always" title="Always">always</a>," but is generally used to express a habit, attitude, or convention which has continued for a long period of time until the present. When you use 一向, you're conveying a sense that "it's always been this way."
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
